<taxonomicName id="C8C714AFD08B888CEB07334B0B680386" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Ischiodon" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ischiodon scutellaris" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="59" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scutellaris">Ischiodon scutellaris</taxonomicName>
(Fabricius), male ZFMK-DIP-00019729: A Habitus, lateral view B Frontal view C Habitus, dorsal view D Labels E Metacoxa and metatrochanter, posterolateral view F Male genitalia: a lateral view b postgonite, outline only (from 
